high_descs: Move to counter right next to the wall.
Pick up the blue rag from the counter.
Look up at the shelf above the counter.
Place the blue rag on the shelf.
Look at the counter below the shelf.
Pick up the yellow rag from the counter.
Look up at the shelf above the counter.
Put the yellow rag on the shelf on top of the blue rag.
anns.task_desc: To move two rags from the counter to the shelf.

high_descs: Step to the right and face the rags on the floor.
Pick up the black rag on the floor.
Look up to face the shelving.
Place the black rag on the bottom right shelf.
Look down to face the rags on the floor.
Pick up the white rag on the floor.
Look up to face the top right shelf.
Place the white rag on the top right shelf.
anns.task_desc: To place two rags that are black and white onto two shelves.

high_descs: Take a step forward toward the shelf.
Pick up the dark cloth from the floor
Hold the dark cloth and look up.
Place the dark cloth on the shelf.
Look down to the cloth on the floor.
Pick up the yellow cloth from the floor.
Hold the yellow cloth and look up.
Place the yellow cloth on the shelf, on top of the dark one.
anns.task_desc: Move two cloths to the shelf.
